# Reporting

Generators, templates, and rendered output - the public deliverable of {{PROJECT_NAME}}.

## Layout
- Report generator script(s) at the room root
- `templates/` - HTML/Markdown/PDF scaffolds
- `samples/` - preserved sample reports per run
- `YYYY-MM-DD_<topic>_<status>.<ext>` - the deliverable for a given run

## Required data points per record
{{REPORT_REQUIRED_FIELDS}}

## Rules
- One file = one run, fully self-contained (no external CDN deps for HTML reports).
- Parse and render are separate steps. The generator does not parse.
- No live database deps - reports are static snapshots.
- No hard-coded paths or run identifiers in templates.
- Reports must open correctly when emailed or posted to a wiki/SharePoint.

